<p>True Sight is a sandbox co-op video game that depends on the communication between players.</p>
<p>We are in a village where you need to complete different tasks such as saving a tree from the fire, clean up the trash, etc.<br/>When you complete the tasks the doors on top will open and you'll be able to fight the Boss.</p>
<p>Move the player on the left with WASD and the player on the right with the arrow keys.</p>
<p>To interact use Q, E or F and for the other player use the left-click mouse.</p>
